			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "- Load up GustavDev/SCL_Main_A\r\n- Go to the Colony Barracks with \"goto 728 16 14\"\r\n- Let the Mistress of Souls finish blessing the Skull Lashers. Do not come too close or interfere.\r\n- Talk to Krustine, Mistress of Souls, after the blessing AD has finished.\r\n- If you attacked Ketheric on the Moonrise rooftop before coming to Colony, the Myrkulites will be hostile to you on sight."
				},
